descriptionHtml:
Master Your Thoughts & Transform Your Life with Marisa Peer

Marisa Peer is the award-winning founder of Rapid Transformational Therapy (RTT®). She's a British therapist, best-selling author, transformational leader, keynote speaker, and creator of the ‘I Am Enough’ movement.

This app is the home of Marisa Peer's Abundant Life membership, 21-day transformational challenges, and many other life-changing self-hypnosis programs, meditation and hypnosis audios.

Join this app to:

+ Be part of the Abundant Life's supportive community of like-minded achievers
+ Have dedicated time with Marisa and your tribe each month to focus on specific topics and experience shifts in all areas of life.
+ Build accountability partnerships and gain opportunities for deep connections.
+ Take part in live guided group meditations to achieve rapid and permanent results.
+ Have a dedicated community manager, available throughout.
+ Gain access to over 50+ self-hypnosis and meditation audios.
+ Take part in Marisa Peer's 21-day transformational challenges to inspire growth as a way of life.

Are you ready to unlock your extraordinary power to live an abundant life?

Download the app and start this transformational journey today.
